OSS License Comprehension Study

Read data

library(dplyr)
userdata <- read.csv("OSSStudy5.csv", header=T)

Eye Fixation data Clustering (MEL + LEL)

  • g1: 1,3,4,5,9
  • g2: 2,6,7,8,10
  • cuttree: 1 2 1 1 1 2 2 2 1 2
df <- scale(select(userdata, matches('melfix|lelfix|switches')))
colnames(df)
 [1] "melfixcnthierachy" "melfixcntmodel"    "melfixcnttask"     "melfixcnttext"     "lelfixcnthierachy" "lelfixcntmodel"   
 [7] "lelfixcnttask"     "lelfixcnttext"     "melfixdurhierachy" "melfixdurmodel"    "melfixdurtask"     "melfixdurtext"    
[13] "lelfixdurhierachy" "lelfixdurmodel"    "lelfixdurtask"     "lelfixdurtext"     "melswitches"       "lelswitches"      
hc <- hclust(dist(df))
groups <- cutree(hc,k =2)
groups <- cbind(userdata$ID, groups)
g1 <- groups[groups[,2] == 1,1]
g1
[1] 1 3 4 5 9
g2 <- groups[groups[,2] == 2,1]
g2
[1]  2  6  7  8 10
h <- heatmap(df, distfun = dist, hclustfun = hclust, scale="none")
